        "text": "Here's the Crystal-idiomatic form:\n\n```crystal\nname.length\n```\n\n**Crystal version:**\n```crystal\nname.length\n```\n\n**Explanation:**\n\nCrystal's stdlib has a `String#length` method (line 1077 of `src/string.cr`) which returns an `Int32`.",
